  Kay
  

Frank Sumption <purplealiengirl@...> wrote:
      .hmmessage P  {  margin:0px;  padding:0px  }  body.hmmessage  {  FONT-SIZE: 10pt;  FONT-FAMILY:Tahoma  }    "The four archangels represent different fields of modern science. Gabriel is the patron of computers and the Internet." From www.pyracantha.com/religious.html
 
 Also " 
The Archangel Gabriel  Archangel of the West and of Water, Gabriel is the Messenger of God. And is well known for his announcement of the birth of Jesus.
He is connected with our emotions, cleansing, loving and intuitive self. And can aid you with your spiritual insight, growth and travels on the astral planes.
Also connected with the Moon, and the sea and all life that is within.If you are working with dolphins, he is your contact.
Present at our births he occasionally turns up at our final transition to ease us through. "
 
 From sanctuary-of-enlightenment.8m.com/photo4.html


 
 A weird Gabriel reference, and a Bruce comment. From a recording done Sunday night. 
 
 Frank-S
